data.description: **PRICE REDUCED**  Welcome to the epitome of luxury and convenience! This fully furnished 11-bedroom oasis nestled within the sought-after Encore at Reunion Resort community is your dream come true. Just a stone's throw away from the magic of Disney, this haven offers an extraordinary blend of elegance and resort-style living that's second to none. On-Site Waterpark, Bar, Restaurant, Sports Courts & More. The expansive open-plan kitchen, dining, and living area is designed with large families in mind, making gatherings and quality time unforgettable. A true retreat, the master suite on the first floor beckons relaxation with sliding doors leading to the covered patio and your private swimming oasis. Imagine lounging by the pool, embracing the Florida sunsets, and enjoying seamless indoor-outdoor living. One of the remarkable features of this property is the converted garage, transformed into an exhilarating games room featuring both pool and hockey tables. Entertain your guests with friendly matches, creating memories that last a lifetime.  With no rear neighbors, you'll relish unparalleled privacy and the luxury of unobstructed views. This gem is a testament to exquisite living in a prime location.  This is Your Moment: Don't let this extraordinary opportunity slip away. Contact your trusted realtor today to arrange a viewing and experience the magic of this remarkable property. Your dream home awaits – seize it now!
